# Welcome to the Delchbump Repository.
# This Repository is for the upcoming FPS game, Delchbump.
This repository contains meshes and scripts used. **This will NOT contain an uncopylocked version of Delchbump.** This will contain scripts and meshes to modify to your heart's content.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
